      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must be performed on a geometry and operating regime directly representative of the VAD COU; FDA generic pump serves as surrogate only.",
      "rationale": "Validation was conducted on the FDA generic centrifugal pump, which is a simplified surrogate. Actual VAD geometry, implant configuration, and patient-representative flow waveforms were not used. Achieved level 2 against required level 5."
