      "acceptanceCriteria": "Justification for choice of hemolysis model (e.g., power-law vs. strain-based) and turbulence closure must be provided with sensitivity analysis.",
      "rationale": "The Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model was selected without documented justification or comparison to alternative model forms. Turbulence model sensitivity analysis absent. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
